{"tha-ap494:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap494:0.2":"Kinkanipupphavagga ","tha-ap494:0.3":"Pamsukulapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap494:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap494:1.2":"udangano nama pabbato; ","tha-ap494:1.3":"Tatthaddasam pamsukulam, ","tha-ap494:1.4":"dumaggamhi vilambitam. ","tha-ap494:2.1":"Tini kinkanipupphani, ","tha-ap494:2.2":"ocinitvanaham tada; ","tha-ap494:2.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap494:2.4":"pamsukulamapujayim. ","tha-ap494:3.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap494:3.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap494:3.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap494:3.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap494:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap494:4.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap494:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap494:4.4":"pujitva arahaddhajam. ","tha-ap494:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap494:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap494:5.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap494:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap494:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap494:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap494:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap494:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap494:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap494:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pamsukulapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap494:9.1":"Pamsukulapujakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}